The Camera is used to take pictures within VRChat. It can be accessed through the Quick Menu, or the Tools tab of the Action Menu. The camera is also used to capture icon, [[Special:MyLanguage/Gallery|gallery]] photos, as well as create [[Special:MyLanguage/Stickers|stickers]] and [[Special:MyLanguage/VRC+#Prints|prints]] from within the client, or on the VRChat website if subscribed to [[Special:MyLanguage/VRChat+|VRC+]]. Users with VRC+ also have access to a [[Special:MyLanguage/Camera Dolly|camera dolly]] for creating customized motions with the camera. On Desktop/PCVR there is an '''Open Photos Folder''' button in the Camera tab that opens VRChat's file directory of where photos/screenshots are stored. To quickly open the camera double-click the Camera icon instead of only once.